aic2024.user

Class AstronautInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • aic2024.user.AstronautInfo

  • public class AstronautInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class with the information of a given astronaut at a given timestamp. Note that the values are immutable, and thus they don't update over time. For example if an astronaut loses oxygen, any UnitInfo associated to that astronaut will not change.
